--------------------------------------------------------------


Catch the sweetheart of the Canadian music scene, Johnny Reid, performing holiday classics and originals this Thursday, Dec. 19, 2013 at 8 et/pt on Global.

The Scottish-born, Canadian-raised, multi-platinum singer/songwriter will perform songs from his latest holiday album "A Christmas Gift to You." Tune in to watch Reid's renditions of "O Holy Night," "Little Drummer Boy," "Have Yourself a Merry Little Christmas" and "Do You Hear What I Hear," among others.

"Christmas is a time of peace, hope, love and happiness," Reid says. "I've always loved Christmas and everything it represents."
